      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind some cosmetic wear. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dings, and the interior shows typical signs of age with some wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it may require some minor maintenance in the near future to keep it in top shape. It\u2019s a solid, functional car offered at a price that reflects its current state.",
