      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. To ensure structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed\u2014critical for long-term mechanical health. The chassis maintains its legendary 50/50 weight distribution, offering telepathic turn-in and exceptional mid-corner balance. While showing honest signs of use, the mechanical systems are sorted, and the induction note remains intoxicating up to the 7,900 RPM redline.",
