    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW 540i xDrive, finished in a sophisticated Sophisto Grey Metallic that catches the light beautifully. As a 'good' condition vehicle, it shows the pride of ownership while reflecting honest, light use. The exterior paint remains vibrant and glossy, with only minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, faint scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch\u2014imperfections consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of Black Dakota leather; the seats are firm and free of cracks, and the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats since day one. This is a strictly non-smoking vehicle with no lingering odors. All technological features, including the iDrive infotainment system, head-up display, and multi-zone climate control, are in perfect working order. Under the hood, the 3.0L turbocharged inline-six engine delivers smooth, effortless power, complemented by a transmission that shifts without hesitation. Maintenance has been performed religiously every 5,000 miles, and the Continental ProContact tires have approximately 70% tread remaining. This car offers a premium driving experience and is ready for its next long-term owner.",
